OL,3,CAsylum in UK to be made temporary
OL,4,Cunder new plans
OL,6,FRefugee status will become temporary
OL,7,Fand subject to regular review under
OL,8,Fthe planned changes, which will see
OL,9,Frefugees removed as soon as their home
OL,10,Fcountries are deemed safe.
OL,12,FUnder current rules, those granted
OL,13,Frefugee status have it for five years
OL,14,Fand can then apply for indefinite
OL,15,Fleave to remain and get on a route to
OL,16,Fcitizenship.
OL,18,FAn ally of the Home Secretary told PA
OL,19,FNews Agency: "Today, becoming a
OL,20,Frefugee equals a lifetime of
OL,21,Fprotection in Britain.
