OL,6,F"Mahmood will change that, making
OL,7,Frefugee status temporary and subject
OL,8,Fto regular review. The moment your
OL,9,Fhome country is safe to return to, you
OL,10,Fwill be removed.
OL,12,F"While this might seem like a small
OL,13,Ftechnical shift, this new settlement
OL,14,Fmarks the most significant shift in
OL,15,Fthe treatment of refugees since the
OL,16,FSecond World War."
