OL,3,CAsylum in UK to be made temporary
OL,4,Cunder new plans
OL,6,FIn a video posted on X on Friday, Ms
OL,7,FMahmood described her plans, to be
OL,8,Fannounced to MPs on Monday, as "the
OL,9,Fmost significant changes to our asylum
OL,10,Fsystem in modern times" and pointed to
OL,11,Frising numbers of asylum claims in
OL,12,FBritain while numbers fall across
OL,13,FEurope.
OL,15,FShe said the previous government had
OL,16,Fhad "years to tackle this problem" but
OL,17,Fhad "wasted" time and money on the
OL,18,F#700 million Rwanda scheme.
