OL,3,CAsylum in UK to be made temporary
OL,4,Cunder new plans
OL,6,FBut under Labour, she said, there had
OL,7,Fbeen "record levels" of immigration
OL,8,Fraids and arrests, and that nearly
OL,9,F50,000 people with no right to be in
OL,10,Fthe UK had been returned.
OL,12,FMigrants continued to arrive in the UK
OL,13,Fafter crossing the English Channel on
OL,14,FFriday. Photographs show men, women
OL,15,Fand children being brought to shore in
OL,16,FDover, with one man sitting at the
OL,17,Fport in a wheelchair.
