OL,3,CAsylum in UK to be made temporary
OL,4,Cunder new plans
OL,6,FSome 39,075 people have arrived in the
OL,7,FUK after making the journey so far
OL,8,Fthis year, according to the latest
OL,9,FHome Office figures.
OL,11,FThe arrivals have already passed the
OL,12,Fnumber for the whole of 2024 (36,816)
OL,13,Fand 2023 (29,437), but the number is
OL,14,Fstill below the total at this point in
OL,15,F2022 (39,929).
