OL,3,CAsylum in UK to be made temporary
OL,4,Cunder new plans
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Government's pilot
OL,7,Fscheme with France aimed at deterring
OL,8,Fpeople from making the dangerous
OL,9,Fcrossing, has removed 113 people to
OL,10,Fthe continent since it was introduced
OL,11,Fin August, while 92 have arrived in
OL,12,Fthe UK under the deal's approved safe
OL,13,Froute.
OL,15,FOther changes expected to be announced
OL,16,Fon Monday include requiring judges to
OL,17,Fprioritise public safety over
OL,18,Fmigrants' rights to a family life, or
OL,19,Fthe risk that they will face "inhuman"
OL,20,Ftreatment if returned to their home
OL,21,Fcountry, according to the Telegraph.
