OL,6,FDenmark's tighter rules on family
OL,7,Freunions are also being looked at.
OL,8,FSome research has suggested that
OL,9,Fdeterrence policies have little impact
OL,10,Fon asylum seekers' choice of
OL,11,Fdestination, but a 2017 study said
OL,12,FDenmark's "negative nation branding"
OL,13,Fhad proved effective in limiting
OL,14,Fasylum applications.
