OL,3,CAsylum in UK to be made temporary
OL,4,Cunder new plans
OL,6,FThe number of asylum applications in
OL,7,Fthe UK is at a record high, as latest
OL,8,FHome Office figures show 111,084
OL,9,Fpeople applied for asylum in the UK in
OL,10,Fthe year to June 2025. This is the
OL,11,Fhighest number for any 12-month period
OL,12,Fsince current records began in 2001.
